<h2 id="topics-for-discussionreflection">Topics for Discussion/Reflection</h2>

<ul>
  <li>How do we deal with renewable energy source intermittency? <br /></li>
  <li>Where do you think DG would have the greatest advantage? <br /></li>
  <li>What do you see as the biggest obstacle to DG? How could it be overcome? <br /></li>
</ul>

